This paper discusses the tracking of user behavior on the web, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of data mining techniques to analyze user data, which falls under the category of information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also discusses the use of machine learning algorithms to predict user behavior, which falls under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the storage and retrieval of user data, which falls under the category of databases (cs.DB). Finally, the paper discusses the use of personalized advertising, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM).
